<h1>How To Start A Digital Business in 2026 (Beginner Guide)</h1>
<p>Starting an online business doesn’t have to be complicated. This simple guide shows you how to build and sell your first digital product step by step.</p>
<h2>Step 1: Choose a Profitable Problem</h2>
<p>Pick a problem people already pay to solve. Look for complaints and questions on Reddit, Facebook groups and Google.</p>
<h2>Step 2: Build a Simple Digital Product</h2>
<p>Create a guide, checklist or workbook that solves one clear problem.</p>
<h2>Step 3: Launch Without Tech Overwhelm</h2>
<p>Use a simple landing page, Stripe and a thank-you page for instant delivery.</p>
<h2>Step 4: Drive Traffic & Make Sales</h2>
<p>Use search engines, Pinterest and forums to get faceless traffic.</p>
